Package model

Class ToDoTask

java.lang.Object
model.ToDoTask
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class ToDoTask
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
The representation of the each task in the to do list. Each task will have its own content, note, the due date, and the location which each respective method of getter and setter.
Author:
Ofer Greenberg, Quan Nguyen, Quang Vu, Allen David El.
